Articles.Content: A few weeks back, before i switched laptop and trashed my old one, I was using a mod that uploaded vessel stats and little gifs of staging and things. Can anyone remember what it was? I've searched the forums and can't find a link. Sorry if this is the wrong section.

I have no idea what you mean.

I'd suggest you browse through http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/50701-community-mods-and-plugins-library/ or one of the many screenshot threads and look if anything looks familiar.
Once you found a screenshot with what you're looking for I am convinced somebody will be able to identify it for you.
